The '''''Capri Nitari''''' was a [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggling]] ship owned by [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Scarlet Bloodhawk]]. It was known to have made the [[Kessel Run/Legends|Kessel Run]] at least once, and made many stops at the planet [[Mandrine/Legends|Mandrine]].

